## Content Visual Style Guide

### LinkedIn Posts
- No stock photos (ever)
- Simple quote graphics with your words
- Carousel with methodology steps (if educational)
- Photo of you (if personal story)

### Profile
- Professional but warm headshot
- Banner that signals niche (authority architect)
- Headline is the offer, not a job title

